    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You point your finger, cursing your target, and the creature that damaged you is momentarily surrounded by hellish flames.</em></p><p><span><strong>Dexterity Save</strong> </span></p><p>You cast this spell when a creature damages you.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 2d10 fire]] damage.*</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting</strong> : Increase damage by [[/damage 1d10 fire]]{1d10} for each spell level above 1st.</p>",
